Bola Tinubu, a chieftain of the All Progressives Congress (APC) and presidential hopeful, is currently in Saudi Arabia for lesser hajj. According to a statement by his campaign organisation, Tinubu left Nigeria around midnight on Monday for Saudi Arabia. Tinubu was said to have arrived Medina in the early hours of Tuesday and is expected to reach Mecca by Tuesday evening. “It has become yearly tradition for the APC presidential aspirant to perform Umrah,” the statement reads. See photos below. <img class="aligncenter wp-image-691536" src="https://f5p3e9e4.stackpathcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/WhatsApp-Image-2022-04-26-at-9.22.23-PM.jpeg" alt="" width="550" height="618" srcset="https://f5p3e9e4.stackpathcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/WhatsApp-Image-2022-04-26-at-9.22.23-PM.jpeg 720w, https://f5p3e9e4.stackpathcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/WhatsApp-Image-2022-04-26-at-9.22.23-PM-267x300.jpeg 267w, https://f5p3e9e4.stackpathcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/WhatsApp-Image-2022-04-26-at-9.22.23-PM-21x24.jpeg 21w, https://f5p3e9e4.stackpathcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/WhatsApp-Image-2022-04-26-at-9.22.23-PM-32x36.jpeg 32w, https://f5p3e9e4.stackpathcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/WhatsApp-Image-2022-04-26-at-9.22.23-PM-43x48.jpeg 43w" sizes="(max-width: 550px) 100vw, 550px" /> <img class="aligncenter wp-image-691537" src="https://f5p3e9e4.stackpathcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/WhatsApp-Image-2022-04-26-at-7.24.14-PM.jpeg" alt="" width="550" height="367" srcset="https://f5p3e9e4.stackpathcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/WhatsApp-Image-2022-04-26-at-7.24.14-PM.jpeg 720w, https://f5p3e9e4.stackpathcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/WhatsApp-Image-2022-04-26-at-7.24.14-PM-300x200.jpeg 300w, https://f5p3e9e4.stackpathcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/WhatsApp-Image-2022-04-26-at-7.24.14-PM-24x16.jpeg 24w, https://f5p3e9e4.stackpathcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/WhatsApp-Image-2022-04-26-at-7.24.14-PM-36x24.jpeg 36w, https://f5p3e9e4.stackp